Package: table1
Title: R package for creating the data summary table for clinical studies using Tufte style
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Amin", "Adibi", email = "amin.adibi@ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Clinical studies often have a table 1 that includes a summary of the data. The package creates publication-quality LaTeX tables with embedded Tufte style graphics. 
Depends: R (>= 3.4.3)
License: GPL3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports:
    graphics,
    ggplot2,
    ggthemes,
    openxlsx,
    reshape2,
    scales,
    tidyverse,
    sparkTable,
    tufte,
    haven
    
